<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Work - My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            background: #005691;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .projects {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .project {
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .project:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .project img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .project h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #005691;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>My Work</h1>
        <nav>
            <%= link_to 'Home', root_path %> |
            <%= link_to 'About Me', about_path %> |
            <%= link_to 'My Work', work_path, class: 'active' %> |
            <%= link_to 'Contact Me', contact_path %>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="projects">
        <div class="project">
            <%= image_tag "socket.jpeg", alt: "Chatbox" %>
            <h3>Chatbox</h3>
            <p>This project involved building a responsive web application using socket programming.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
            <%= image_tag "auction.jpeg", alt: "Auction" %>
            <h3>Auction</h3>
            <p>An auction platform designed with Ruby on Rails, featuring  bid and payment gateway integration.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Explore the projects to see the quality and diversity of my work. Reach out if you want more detailed information!</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

